    <item>
      <title>共和党强硬派强制投票罢免议长约翰逊</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/gop-hardliners-plan-to-force-vote-on-deposing-speaker-johnson</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名共和党强硬派周三宣布，他们将强制投票罢免众议院议长迈克·约翰逊(Mike Johnson)，这场战斗他们几乎肯定会失败，同时会在一个严重分裂的政党中激起意识形态敌意。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/gop-hardliners-plan-to-force-vote-on-deposing-speaker-johnson</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 13:26:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>总理表示马来西亚将创纪录地提高政府工资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/malaysia-plans-to-raise-government-worker-salaries-from-december</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣 (Anwar Ibrahim) 表示，为应对不断上涨的生活成本和疲软的货币，该国将从 12 月起将公务员的工资提高 13% 以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/malaysia-plans-to-raise-government-worker-salaries-from-december</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 08:28:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
